{"tid":1536600,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我已經好努力 希望你哋幫我打下氣","createTime":"2019-09-03T16:35:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T23:58:04.000Z","uid":186849,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"9e865b94e63e81a0770e771c787bd13460621936","tid":1536600,"uid":186849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:35:41.000Z","msg":"我做咩事都係為人哋諗咗先<br />\n我唔識得有啲咁嘅下場<br />\n明明已經冇得一齊住<br />\n點解仲要發我脾氣<br />\n而一齊住嘅人唔識珍惜<br />\n因為政治立場同意而嘈<br />\n<br />\n我好畀心機我畀心機啦各位巴打絲打<br />\n我每個月自己 連買埋粒糖都唔捨得<br />\n但係點解我得嚟嘅 喺咁既生活<br />\n<br />\n時代愈動盪<br />\n只有 相互體諒 先至會捱得過<br />\n我好似抖唔到氣咁<br />\n<br />\n一年前起我已經想自殺<br />\n好辛苦好辛苦咁捱過咗<br />\n做咗四年嘢 工一份接一份<br />\nNon stop咁返 係一日都右放假咁樣工接工返落去<br />\n<br />\n點解我要受氣？<br />\n點解我得到啲咁嘅生活"},{"pid":"844caa7b7c1fa2877802d0c1fb5f4ff98d438cf8","tid":1536600,"uid":186849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:37:10.000Z","msg":"我究竟做錯咗啲乜嘢先至會落嚟呢個人間地獄<br />\n其實我用開心好簡單<br />\n畀多啲溫暖我體諒我<br />\n我同你食麥當勞都會好開心"},{"pid":"7d71a5b314dfe4035478840d8cfb38c98d3d1d3c","tid":1536600,"uid":73550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:37:23.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea26bd531a9fb5381610b1a5ecda44b756da28a1","tid":1536600,"uid":186849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d71a5b314dfe4035478840d8cfb38c98d3d1d3c","tid":1536600,"uid":73550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:37:23.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:37:44.000Z","msg":"多謝"},{"pid":"9850915cc26ca4069a4c89d4d42b102c8712a249","tid":1536600,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:37:46.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"62599aad2e961e392bc6f6f9ed8f0f5c04849f15","tid":1536600,"uid":300767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:40:05.000Z","msg":"加油!!!!對自己好d先對別人好~~~~"},{"pid":"f04a39b2217b2d70ca28c4e987a306b53a163782","tid":1536600,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:40:06.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借位一用<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">【Google 廣告】上線啦 !</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dOiORS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dOiORS</a>"},{"pid":"755d23f404fa69f8293a174e57c34ac126730b5e","tid":1536600,"uid":130214,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:53:58.000Z","msg":"價值觀唔同 及早分開<br />\