而起衝突<br />\n我會覺得暫時分別吓會好啲<br />\n一齊住既 睇吓搵唔搵到第二度住<br />\n分開一陣可以減少衝突<br />\n同時 &ldquo;一日不見如隔三秋&rdquo;嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能分開吓會令雙方更思念更珍惜呢<br />\n<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd79aeea046223084cef45ae82531fea160591f","tid":1536600,"uid":32505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:15:42.000Z","msg":"休息是為了走更長遠的路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乖 去放返個𡃁假先<br />\n唔好諗咁多 去玩下食下啦 係時候錫下自己<br />\n辛苦哂你啦"},{"pid":"0a2d7e6351d455908898521bef96d79d3d980078","tid":1536600,"uid":33694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:17:22.000Z","msg":"巴打我地會陪你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d137f6a9fb9eef6e942a0b82b8a841bfd376a21","tid":1536600,"uid":279874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e865b94e63e81a0770e771c787bd13460621936","tid":1536600,"uid":186849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:35:41.000Z","msg":"我做咩事都係為人哋諗咗先<br />\n我唔識得有啲咁嘅下場<br />\n明明已經冇得一齊住<br />\n點解仲要發我脾氣<br />\n而一齊住嘅人唔識珍惜<br />\n因為政治立場同意而嘈<br />\n<br />\n我好畀心機我畀心機啦各位巴打絲打<br />\n我每個月自己 連買埋粒糖都唔捨得<br />\n但係點解我得嚟嘅 喺咁既生活<br />\n<br />\n時代愈動盪<br />\n只有 相互體諒 先至會捱得過<br />\n我好似抖唔到氣咁<br />\n<br />\n一年前起我已經想自殺<br />\n好辛苦好辛苦咁捱過咗<br />\n做咗四年嘢 工一份接一份<br />\nNon stop咁返 係一日都右放假咁樣工接工返落去<br />\n<br />\n點解我要受氣？<br />\n點解我得到啲咁嘅生活"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:19:52.000Z","msg":"加油呀，放鬆吓，其實我做咗十年嘢都係工接工咁返㗎。有時返工係好辛苦，但只係打工者，要自己調節一吓，放工就唔好再理工作啦。<br />\n至於政見，其實每個人都活咗咁耐，唔係話聽你講幾句就可以輕易改變到，我全家都藍嘅，咁我咪講到明喺屋企唔講政治囉，如果你想搵人傾，上嚟大把人同你傾呀，頂住呀"},{"pid":"44be576f28b4cf078b7e61318ce76d5b0ef89e0d","tid":1536600,"uid":136233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:20:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a4e44431bbe2b8ca9a36c0e1f4052827b83a48c9","tid":1536600,"uid":85965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:20:51.000Z","msg":"巴打已經好努力<br />\n我唔識開解人<br />\n但我覺得總有同路人<br />\n只係你而家未遇到"},{"pid":"4f0b1a75d21bc5dc6d88612997490c9cdef04f03","tid":1536600,"uid":186849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1806a6af7893eb468d378374c714a5f1f71fdb3","tid":1536600,"uid":251314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:05:20.000Z","msg":"一齊向前走，同佢地鬥長命！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:21:55.000Z","msg":"攰"},{"pid":"8ca3c4afe06d2b1dca1bcbd45b1d09296e291660","tid":1536600,"uid":186849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91315036c410f1b9f3c74fc49e17fd756447d495","tid":1536600,"uid":55384,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:05:24.000Z","msg":"放個假休息下,唔好睇新聞<br />\n依幾個月真係好負能量,本身抗體差既人真係會好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:22:05.000Z","msg":"要錢"},{"pid":"6942a7c21036a320a939bce3d60ed7082d8a95dd","tid":1536600,"uid":186849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd3382e75fb7ab9d7178e7fc9d834c23561ce457","tid":1536600,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:05:25.000Z","msg":"出黎屌下黑警 有咩唔順超鬧爆佢地就得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:22:38.000Z","msg":"藍絲家人<br />\n唉<br />\n同埋而家仲未搵到工"},{"pid":"60f51ba4bad1323a2d0bbee0a171c7f24a53bf70","tid":1536600,"uid":186849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efc3f72dad4e192059c9e91912433177e45246de","tid":1536600,"uid":250721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:05:35.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:22:48.000Z","msg":"多謝"},{"pid":"2675706ef09118728a7b710836fb50406b217156","tid":1536600,"uid":186849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3eab7aa5a6bd3e66b5585974f363e487656846f","tid":1536600,"uid":64288,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:06:29.000Z","msg":"我們與你同在"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime"