/>\n<br />\n一年前起我已經想自殺<br />\n好辛苦好辛苦咁捱過咗<br />\n做咗四年嘢 工一份接一份<br />\nNon stop咁返 係一日都右放假咁樣工接工返落去<br />\n<br />\n點解我要受氣？<br />\n點解我得到啲咁嘅生活"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:19:52.000Z","msg":"加油呀，放鬆吓，其實我做咗十年嘢都係工接工咁返㗎。有時返工係好辛苦，但只係打工者，要自己調節一吓，放工就唔好再理工作啦。<br />\n至於政見，其實每個人都活咗咁耐，唔係話聽你講幾句就可以輕易改變到，我全家都藍嘅，咁我咪講到明喺屋企唔講政治囉，如果你想搵人傾，上嚟大把人同你傾呀，頂住呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:24:28.000Z","msg":"好撚感動"},{"pid":"3bb199c141d746568423d5fb1b3fcd12dd16d2c9","tid":1536600,"uid":186849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44be576f28b4cf078b7e61318ce76d5b0ef89e0d","tid":1536600,"uid":136233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:20:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:24:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef9b721116064d2a82444a7d36a9b713b14adb5","tid":1536600,"uid":910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:24:49.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"aff249923f0262d9689895625dc9406632ba2939","tid":1536600,"uid":186849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4e44431bbe2b8ca9a36c0e1f4052827b83a48c9","tid":1536600,"uid":85965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:20:51.000Z","msg":"巴打已經好努力<br />\n我唔識開解人<br />\n但我覺得總有同路人<br />\n只係你而家未遇到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:24:54.000Z","msg":"連登有愛"},{"pid":"54c74e43bfaff569e1dc142f453cbaafd53676f2","tid":1536600,"uid":307607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:25:17.000Z","msg":"加油 大家一齊撐落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aae33fa49c37ccde6d7f8c28a1e3c35d519070aa","tid":1536600,"uid":281585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:26:37.000Z","msg":"唔好放棄啊！！！！<br />\n我哋已經失去好多啦<br />\n唔想連你都失去埋<br />\n答應我唔好做傻事，唔係嬲死你！！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img